140
00:06:12,122 --> 00:06:15,676
az m'hot dos ibergelebt, az m'hot dos ibergehaltn

141
00:06:18,906 --> 00:06:21,181
az ir zayt fun Malkin

142
00:06:21,181 --> 00:06:23,929
keyn,

143
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:29,036
