199
00:08:40,279 --> 00:08:42,499
un zey hobn undz avekgefirt in a lager arayn.

200
00:08:43,457 --> 00:08:45,796
zey hobn undz gekhapt, gefirt azoy vi a

201
00:08:46,309 --> 00:08:50,437
m'hot undz gefirt zeks vokhn. mir zenen mir geforn mit KONSKI vagonen.

202
00:08:50,933 --> 00:08:51,922
biz

203
00:08:51,743 --> 00:08:54,099
biz in a lager, STANTSIYA YAYA.

204
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:56,546
vu, dos iz in Sibir?

205
00:08:56,029 --> 00:08:57,018
Sibir.

206
00:08:57,700 --> 00:09:02,134
un in di ts- in dem, durkh dem yor vos ir zent geven in tfise

207
