208
00:09:05,344 --> 00:09:07,987
kh'hob finef yor nisht gevust in gantsn vu er iz.

209
00:09:07,757 --> 00:09:08,915
finef yor?

210
00:09:08,432 --> 00:09:09,438
finef yor.

211
